---
import PageShell from "../components/layout/PageShell.astro";
import Badge from "../components/ui/Badge.astro";
import Button from "../components/ui/Button.astro";
import Card from "../components/ui/Card.astro";
import { picturebookPages, villageAnimals } from "../data/animalSkin";
import { routeSeo } from "../data/seo";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { sitePath } from "../utils/paths";

const picturebookCover = picturebookPages[0];
const heroCover = "/images/picturebook-skin/picturebook/block-village-v1/picturebook-block-village-wechat-cover.png";
---

<BaseLayout {...routeSeo["/"]} analyticsEvent="home_view" analyticsProps={{ path: "/" }}>
  <PageShell>
    <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="hero-title">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <Badge tone="yellow">方块村魔方启蒙</Badge>
          <h1 id="hero-title">
            玩转魔方，<br class="mobile-title-break" />有手就行。
          </h1>
          <p>8 个关卡一步一步走，先看图，再动手。</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <Button href="/levels" analyticsEvent="levels_click" analyticsProps={{ source_path: "/", source_label: "home_hero" }}>开始学习路径</Button>
            <Button href="/picturebook" variant="secondary" analyticsEvent="picturebook_click" analyticsProps={{ source_path: "/", source_label: "home_hero" }}>先看方块村绘本</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img class="hero-cover" src={sitePath(heroCover)} alt="方块村动物围着魔方的横向绘本封面" loading="eager" />
      </div>
      <section class="intro-principle" aria-labelledby="intro-principle-title">
        <Badge tone="green">项目意义</Badge>
        <h2 id="intro-principle-title">从一个小魔方开始，练习“我能”</h2>
        <p>完整复原太难，就拆成 8 个小目标。孩子先完成一张任务卡，再慢慢建立信心。</p>
      </section>
    </section>

    <section class="village-entry" aria-labelledby="village-title">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <Badge tone="yellow">方块村</Badge>
        <h2 id="village-title">先认识 6 个颜色家的小居民</h2>
        <p>孩子可以先看绘本，再回到 8 关地图；每一关仍然只解决一个清楚的魔方目标。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="village-layout">
        <a class="picturebook-card" href={sitePath("/picturebook")} aria-label="打开方块村魔方绘本">
          <img src={sitePath(picturebookCover.src)} alt={picturebookCover.alt} loading="lazy" />
          <span>魔方绘本</span>
          <strong>方块村被转乱的一天</strong>
        </a>
        <div class="animal-roster" aria-label="方块村居民">
          {
            villageAnimals.map((animal) => (
              <div class="animal-chip">
                <img src={sitePath(animal.avatar)} alt={animal.alt} loading="lazy" />
                <div>
                  <strong>{animal.name}</strong>
                  <span>{animal.home}</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="meaning-grid" aria-labelledby="meaning-heading">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <Badge tone="green">为什么做</Badge>
        <h2 id="meaning-heading">把困难铺成孩子能走上去的踏板</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="cards-grid">
        <Card>
          <h3>不是一次复原，是一次一关</h3>
          <p>完整复原魔方对孩子来说链条太长。这个网站把大目标拆成清楚的关卡，每一关只看一个目标、做一个动作、确认一个结果。</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3>用非屏幕玩具训练注意力</h3>
          <p>魔方适合在车上、排队、吃饭等待时拿出来练。它像一个小哑铃，训练观察、方向判断和持续控制自己的手。</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3>让家长也能参与身教</h3>
          <p>遇到难题时，家长的回应本身就是示范。我们不绕开困难，而是把困难画清楚、拆小、陪孩子一起完成。</p>
        </Card>
        <Card>
          <h3>最终要留下“我能”的感觉</h3>
          <p>当孩子亲手把一个混乱的魔方复原成整齐的六面，得到的不只是结果，还有一种真实的成就感。</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </section>

  </PageShell>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 247, 224, 0.72), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96) 54%),
      var(--color-surface);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-content,
  .hero-copy,
  .section-heading,
  .meaning-grid,
  .village-entry {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-copy p,
  .section-heading p {
    max-width: 62ch;
  }

  .hero-copy h1 {
    max-width: 10em;
  }

  .mobile-title-break {
    display: block;
  }

  .hero-actions,
  .village-layout,
  .animal-roster {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .hero-cover {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 360px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(39, 39, 42, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: #f7ead2;
  }

  .intro-principle {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-content: start;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(39, 39, 42, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .intro-principle p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .intro-principle h2 {
    max-width: 12em;
  }

  .cards-grid,
  .card-actions {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .village-entry {
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border: 1px solid rgba(219, 151, 46, 0.24);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 247, 224, 0.78), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)),
      var(--color-surface);
  }

  .picturebook-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    min-width: 0;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .picturebook-card img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-height: 360px;
    object-fit: contain;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: #f7ead2;
  }

  .picturebook-card span {
    color: var(--color-muted-text);
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .animal-roster {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .animal-chip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 48px minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-items: center;
    min-width: 0;
    padding: var(--space-sm);
    border: 1px solid rgba(39, 39, 42, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
  }

  .animal-chip img {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .animal-chip div {
    display: grid;
    gap: 2px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .animal-chip span {
    color: var(--color-muted-text);
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
  }

  @media (min-width: 720px) {
    .hero,
    .meaning-grid,
    .village-entry {
      padding: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .hero {
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .hero-content {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.95fr) minmax(280px, 1.05fr);
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .hero-actions {
      grid-template-columns: max-content max-content;
    }

    .mobile-title-break {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero-cover {
      max-height: 420px;
    }

    .village-layout {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(240px, 0.42fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .animal-roster {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }
</style>
